{"tid":839267,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【#Cult片】Troma出品超重口味禁片《Blood Sucking Freaks》（1976）","createTime":"2018-09-27T22:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T03:28:32.000Z","uid":212112,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"06f44114902380fe1f465a1215e064a522a3096f","tid":839267,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T22:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/060657_e647651323d43f3db852826ced260fc2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F060657_e647651323d43f3db852826ced260fc2.png&h=3ac88c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇情講述舞台劇團導演在Soho區的陰暗角落經營一家地下劇場，這裡所表演都與虐待有關。舞台上，被剝去衣服的年輕女性痛苦哀號，面無表情的表演者對她們進行虐打、鋸手、夾手指、挖眼乃至夾頭等酷刑。表演殘酷逼真，觀眾們看得心驚肉跳。<br />\n後來劇團導演將觀眾綁架，通過無休止的虐待來滿足自己那瘋狂而扭曲的慾望⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/060658_66d58ba8dd77ceda357c17a3e0223cad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F060658_66d58ba8dd77ceda357c17a3e0223cad.png&h=bc904347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n單純論電影劇情尚算有趣，但是令人不解的是片中出現的女性角色，每一個彷如死魚般，完全沒有表情和自我意識，隨劇團導演的擺佈演出各種情節，電影中的女性幾乎完全裸露肉體，在透過變態劇情上玩辱女體，包括明顯的乳頭夾夾子然後通電，即屁股劃上紅心，拿起飛鏢一隻一隻飛往肥厚的屁股去，完全物化瓦解女性尊嚴及囂張宣洩沙文主義。<br />\n雖說本影片道具和特效在今天看來特别假，但據說這片子本身算得上是日後各種SM電影的鼻祖級作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/060659_fe740a39a54faeec2dd1e250dead6da1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F060659_fe740a39a54faeec2dd1e250dead6da1.png&h=b1a34be5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/060700_822a058aef15c79a8eadf0682fe3ee2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F060700_822a058aef15c79a8eadf0682fe3ee2f.png&h=a6c1cae5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/20